Exercise task: (The file explains how to connect and gives the command to change hostname)

Create small script that will:

1. Connect to Fortigate

2. Read IP from command line
    Either:

    show system interface

    or:

    show system interface ?

3. Read admin credentials from CLI
    get system admin

4. Change the hostname (again, read from command line):

    config system global
        set hostname MYHOSTNAME
    end






